  "body": "### Description of the Issue\r\n\r\nWhen entering info into a swap, the from field seems to be highlighted in red like it's errorous with no message. However, you can still submit the swap.\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Go to /swap\r\n2. Select ETH -> BTC\r\n3. Enter `1` into ETH\r\n4. Blur the input, confirm it's red\r\n5. Click the continue button, confirm it submits anyway\r\n\r\n### Console Logs / Screenshots\r\n\r\n![screen shot 2018-03-20 at 11 47 38 am](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/649992/37665941-ba4d0774-2c34-11e8-8b0e-d55be6098eb9.png)",
